graph TB
    subgraph "RHODS Operator (redhat-ods-operator-system)"
        Manager[Operator Manager<br/>Go Controller Runtime]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]

        subgraph "Component Controllers"
            DashboardCtrl[Dashboard Controller]
            KServeCtrl[KServe Controller]
            PipelinesCtrl[Data Science Pipelines Controller]
            RayCtrl[Ray Controller]
            TrainingCtrl[Training Operator Controller]
            WorkbenchesCtrl[Workbenches Controller]
            ModelRegCtrl[Model Registry Controller]
            TrustyAICtrl[TrustyAI Controller]
        end

        subgraph "Platform Controllers"
            DSCICtrl[DSCInitialization Controller]
            DSCCtrl[DataScienceCluster Controller]
            AuthCtrl[Auth Service Controller]
            MonitoringCtrl[Monitoring Service Controller]
            GatewayCtrl[Gateway Config Controller]
        end

        Manager -->|manages| DashboardCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| KServeCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| PipelinesCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| RayCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| TrainingCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| WorkbenchesCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| ModelRegCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| TrustyAICtrl
        Manager -->|manages| DSCICtrl
        Manager -->|manages| DSCCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| AuthCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| MonitoringCtrl
        Manager -->|manages| GatewayCtrl
    end

    User[Platform Admin] -->|creates| DSC_CR[DataScienceCluster CR]
    User -->|creates| DSCI_CR[DSCInitialization CR]

    DSC_CR -->|validated by| Webhook
    DSCI_CR -->|validated by| Webhook

    DSC_CR -->|watched by| DSCCtrl
    DSCI_CR -->|watched by| DSCICtrl

    DSCCtrl -->|creates| ComponentCRs[Component CRs<br/>Dashboard, KServe, Ray, etc.]
    DSCICtrl -->|creates| ServiceCRs[Service CRs<br/>Auth, Monitoring, Gateway]

    ComponentCRs -->|watched by| DashboardCtrl
    ComponentCRs -->|watched by| KServeCtrl
    ComponentCRs -->|watched by| RayCtrl

    ServiceCRs -->|watched by| AuthCtrl
    ServiceCRs -->|watched by| MonitoringCtrl

    DashboardCtrl -->|creates| DashboardDeploy[Dashboard Deployment]
    KServeCtrl -->|deploys| KServeOperator[KServe Operator]
    PipelinesCtrl -->|deploys| DSPOperator[DSP Operator]
    RayCtrl -->|deploys| RayOperator[Ray Operator]

    Manager -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Manager -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh]
    Manager -.->|optional| Serverless[OpenShift Serverless]
    Manager -.->|optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>redhat-ods-monitoring]

    style Manager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Metrics fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style DSCCtrl fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSCICtrl fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSC_CR fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSCI_CR fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceMesh fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Serverless fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style PrometheusOp fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
